| ----------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| **Protein Accuracy**                | Updated backbone & side-chain parameters; highly accurate | Accurate, but older versions may drift in loops | Moderate; side-chain accuracy variable | Less accurate for modern systems |
| **Multi-Chain/Interface Stability** | High; preserves inter-chain contacts                      | Moderate                                        | Moderate                               | Poor for large complexes         |
| **Ion & Water Models**              | Modern, stable in EM/MD                                   | Accurate, fewer updates for ions                | Standard, may need tuning              | Older, less realistic            |
